WEBVTT

00:00:00.880 --> 00:00:03.110
Good afternoon and good evening,

00:00:03.120 --> 00:00:05.110
family. Thank you for joining us again

00:00:05.120 --> 00:00:07.269
today. We're just going to go

00:00:07.279 --> 00:00:09.589
right into prayer; I won't keep you all

00:00:09.599 --> 00:00:11.749
too long. I told D,

00:00:11.759 --> 00:00:13.509
'Let's surprise them and come on early

00:00:13.519 --> 00:00:16.230
today and see how the crowds

00:00:16.230 --> 00:00:16.240
are.'We've

00:00:16.240 --> 00:00:18.070
never really been on in the

00:00:18.080 --> 00:00:20.230
afternoons before. We always wait until

00:00:20.240 --> 00:00:22.950
the evenings so Australia can pray

00:00:22.960 --> 00:00:25.509
with us; they're usually

00:00:25.519 --> 00:00:27.589
in the middle of

00:00:27.599 --> 00:00:29.349
their day. I know

00:00:29.359 --> 00:00:31.109
a lot of people from Australia and New Zealand pray with

00:00:31.119 --> 00:00:34.229
us the later we get.

00:00:35.440 --> 00:00:37.190
We thought we would pray with

00:00:37.190 --> 00:00:37.200
you

00:00:37.200 --> 00:00:39.510
this afternoon and

00:00:39.520 --> 00:00:43.510
see who comes;

00:00:43.510 --> 00:00:43.520
it

00:00:43.520 --> 00:00:45.670
might be some from Europe.

00:00:45.680 --> 00:00:49.670
We have a lot

00:00:49.680 --> 00:00:52.310
to talk about. In our

00:00:52.320 --> 00:00:54.709
last prayer call,

00:00:54.719 --> 00:00:57.110
the

00:00:57.120 --> 00:00:59.750
Lord showed us a lot concerning

00:00:59.760 --> 00:01:04.469
this war and praying over our

00:01:04.479 --> 00:01:08.710
military men and women.

00:01:08.720 --> 00:01:11.670
That was a lot of detail,

00:01:11.680 --> 00:01:13.750
but the Lord will not allow me to go

00:01:13.760 --> 00:01:16.070
into much

00:01:16.070 --> 00:01:16.080
of it.

00:01:16.080 --> 00:01:18.469
I'll talk about

00:01:18.479 --> 00:01:21.910
some of the details I was shown.

00:01:46.159 --> 00:01:47.830
We were

00:01:47.840 --> 00:01:51.350
shown more about hotels on the

00:01:51.360 --> 00:01:55.670
Chicago riverfront, and I saw a

00:01:55.680 --> 00:01:59.109
major explosive device—I'll say it

00:01:59.119 --> 00:02:01.429
like that for the YouTube

00:02:01.439 --> 00:02:04.550
live—that

00:02:04.560 --> 00:02:06.469
went off in the middle of the

00:02:06.479 --> 00:02:07.990
hotel.

00:02:08.000 --> 00:02:10.229
There were two buildings

00:02:10.239 --> 00:02:13.190
side by side on a riverfront that were a

00:02:13.200 --> 00:02:16.710
hotel. I do not know what this is,

00:02:16.710 --> 00:02:16.720
but

00:02:16.720 --> 00:02:19.030
it looked like a black

00:02:19.030 --> 00:02:19.040
building.

00:02:19.040 --> 00:02:20.390
We'll go over that, and then

00:02:20.390 --> 00:02:20.400
we'll

00:02:20.400 --> 00:02:22.710
go over the Illuminati and what I

00:02:22.720 --> 00:02:24.710
saw about that;

00:02:24.720 --> 00:02:25.830
we'll just do the highlights

00:02:25.830 --> 00:02:25.840
and

00:02:25.840 --> 00:02:27.110
jump right into

00:02:27.120 --> 00:02:30.309
prayer.

00:02:41.120 --> 00:02:42.949
Let's go into what I saw

00:02:42.959 --> 00:02:45.589
about the aircraft carrier, the

00:02:45.599 --> 00:02:47.990
Abraham Lincoln.

00:02:48.000 --> 00:02:49.750
I don't know

00:02:49.760 --> 00:02:51.270
the difference between aircraft

00:02:51.280 --> 00:02:52.710
carriers,

00:02:54.160 --> 00:02:57.990
but I heard the

00:02:57.990 --> 00:02:58.000
name

00:02:58.000 --> 00:03:02.070
Abraham Lincoln and to pray over that

00:03:02.080 --> 00:03:05.910
particular boat.

00:03:05.920 --> 00:03:09.270
I saw another boat that

00:03:09.280 --> 00:03:12.390
was part of its entourage,

00:03:14.080 --> 00:03:15.830
like its

00:03:15.840 --> 00:03:19.350
buddies,

00:03:19.360 --> 00:03:22.869
attached to the Abraham Lincoln.

00:03:26.319 --> 00:03:30.550
When I was shown this explosion,

00:03:30.550 --> 00:03:30.560
it

00:03:30.560 --> 00:03:34.070
took place in the

00:03:34.080 --> 00:03:35.990
middle of that

00:03:35.990 --> 00:03:36.000
smaller

00:03:36.000 --> 00:03:39.030
boat off to the side.

00:03:39.040 --> 00:03:42.149
It was a

00:03:42.159 --> 00:03:45.350
long boat, and I could see

00:03:45.360 --> 00:03:50.949
the crew members being

00:03:50.959 --> 00:03:55.030
shot into the air. I

00:03:55.040 --> 00:03:56.949
don't know if they have anti-aircraft

00:03:56.959 --> 00:03:59.270
missiles on the inside

00:03:59.280 --> 00:04:01.350
that would protect

00:04:11.680 --> 00:04:13.270
them.

00:04:23.040 --> 00:04:25.430
In the

00:04:25.440 --> 00:04:28.230
middle of the flight deck where

00:04:28.240 --> 00:04:31.590
the planes take off,

00:04:31.600 --> 00:04:33.830
something came

00:04:33.840 --> 00:04:37.590
from above—whether it was a drone or

00:04:37.590 --> 00:04:37.600
a

00:04:37.600 --> 00:04:39.909
missile—and

00:04:39.919 --> 00:04:42.230
it caused

00:04:42.240 --> 00:04:45.189
the whole flight deck to explode.

00:04:53.280 --> 00:04:57.110
I saw crew

00:04:57.120 --> 00:05:00.150
members being blown off

00:05:00.160 --> 00:05:02.070
that deck and

00:05:02.080 --> 00:05:04.710
scattered all over the place.

00:05:07.680 --> 00:05:09.830
That's what happened

00:05:09.840 --> 00:05:12.790
in this vision; that was the moment

00:05:12.800 --> 00:05:15.830
I saw our crew members being

00:05:15.840 --> 00:05:18.390
taken out that way, and that's what we

00:05:18.400 --> 00:05:22.070
were praying for. Do we see an

00:05:22.080 --> 00:05:25.029
escalation so far? No.

00:05:25.039 --> 00:05:27.110
I'm

00:05:27.120 --> 00:05:29.749
believing we will have a liberation of

00:05:29.759 --> 00:05:31.990
the people without anybody

00:05:31.990 --> 00:05:32.000
getting

00:05:32.000 --> 00:05:34.469
hurt. When we

00:05:34.479 --> 00:05:36.070
were interceding yesterday, I prayed

00:05:36.070 --> 00:05:36.080
that we would

00:05:36.080 --> 00:05:37.909
not

00:05:37.919 --> 00:05:40.790
see anybody go to war and that

00:05:40.790 --> 00:05:40.800
they would

00:05:40.800 --> 00:05:44.710
disarm

00:05:44.710 --> 00:05:44.720
themselves,

00:05:44.720 --> 00:05:47.189
give away their nuclear

00:05:47.199 --> 00:05:48.629
program,

00:05:48.639 --> 00:05:50.390
and there would be

00:05:50.400 --> 00:05:52.710
liberation for the people.

00:05:52.720 --> 00:05:53.990
In the natural, you might

00:05:53.990 --> 00:05:54.000
ask,

00:05:54.000 --> 00:05:55.270
'Brandon, is that

00:05:55.270 --> 00:05:55.280
possible?'Yes,

00:05:55.280 --> 00:05:57.749
all things are possible

00:05:57.759 --> 00:06:00.469
because I know Ezekiel 38 and 39 is about

00:06:00.479 --> 00:06:03.189
to take place.

00:06:03.199 --> 00:06:05.590
What does that look like if we

00:06:05.600 --> 00:06:07.990
had a

00:06:08.000 --> 00:06:11.909
regime change in Iran?

00:06:11.919 --> 00:06:13.350
I don't add to or

00:06:13.360 --> 00:06:15.189
take away from anything; all I know is

00:06:15.199 --> 00:06:17.670
this is what I saw. I saw other

00:06:17.680 --> 00:06:20.390
things concerning this that I cannot

00:06:20.400 --> 00:06:24.390
talk about, but these were the main things

00:06:24.400 --> 00:06:26.469
I can share

00:06:26.479 --> 00:06:28.790
publicly.

00:06:30.319 --> 00:06:32.469
We

00:06:34.639 --> 00:06:36.390
need to pray for them to really

00:06:36.400 --> 00:06:39.029
be on alert because I saw this

00:06:39.039 --> 00:06:40.230
stuff and thought, 'How do you pray

00:06:40.240 --> 00:06:41.909
into

00:06:41.909 --> 00:06:41.919
that?'I

00:06:41.919 --> 00:06:44.790
bounce these things off

00:06:44.800 --> 00:06:47.350
my team here,

00:06:47.360 --> 00:06:49.270
and

00:06:49.280 --> 00:06:51.189
we want to stop this because

00:06:51.189 --> 00:06:51.199
it

00:06:51.199 --> 00:06:54.150
is very serious

00:06:54.150 --> 00:06:54.160
for

00:06:54.160 --> 00:06:56.390
our servicemen and women.

00:07:02.479 --> 00:07:05.510
The other

00:07:05.520 --> 00:07:07.909
thing I was shown was

00:07:07.919 --> 00:07:12.469
the hotels and the glass fronts.

00:07:12.479 --> 00:07:16.309
It looked like

00:07:16.319 --> 00:07:19.749
a black glass building.

00:07:19.759 --> 00:07:23.510
There

00:07:23.510 --> 00:07:23.520
were

00:07:23.520 --> 00:07:25.909
two buildings

00:07:25.919 --> 00:07:28.550
that looked like twin towers.

00:07:28.560 --> 00:07:32.150
I know it was a

00:07:32.160 --> 00:07:34.710
hotel because the Lord said,

00:07:34.710 --> 00:07:34.720
'This

00:07:34.720 --> 00:07:36.629
is

00:07:36.629 --> 00:07:36.639
a

00:07:36.639 --> 00:07:38.230
hotel.'It

00:07:38.240 --> 00:07:42.469
was on the riverfront of Chicago.

00:07:45.440 --> 00:07:50.870
When this device went off in the middle of the building, it caused

00:07:50.880 --> 00:07:53.189
mass glass to shatter and everything

00:07:53.199 --> 00:07:56.230
was on fire.

00:08:01.039 --> 00:08:03.270
It looked like a

00:08:03.280 --> 00:08:05.430
complete loss.

00:08:05.440 --> 00:08:08.950
As the firefighters and emergency

00:08:08.960 --> 00:08:12.070
responders were coming in,

00:08:12.070 --> 00:08:12.080
I

00:08:12.080 --> 00:08:14.150
saw

00:08:14.150 --> 00:08:14.160
an

00:08:14.160 --> 00:08:17.510
individual on another building

00:08:17.520 --> 00:08:22.309
with a 30-06 style rifle. It had a wood stock;

00:08:22.319 --> 00:08:24.469
it wasn't military-looking like an

00:08:24.479 --> 00:08:28.150
AR. It was a

00:08:28.150 --> 00:08:28.160
wood

00:08:28.160 --> 00:08:31.510
stock

00:08:31.520 --> 00:08:35.269
gun

00:08:35.279 --> 00:08:37.670
with a smaller scope.

00:08:37.670 --> 00:08:37.680
This

00:08:37.680 --> 00:08:38.870
was

00:08:38.870 --> 00:08:38.880
a

00:08:38.880 --> 00:08:40.790
normal-looking

00:08:40.800 --> 00:08:43.509
scope

00:08:46.000 --> 00:08:49.350
on this firearm. He was

00:08:49.360 --> 00:08:52.070
all in black,

00:08:52.080 --> 00:08:54.630
ready to take out emergency

00:08:54.640 --> 00:08:57.430
responders. I

00:08:57.440 --> 00:08:59.829
saw one firefighter

00:08:59.839 --> 00:09:02.870
drop immediately because

00:09:02.880 --> 00:09:05.750
of this individual.

00:09:05.760 --> 00:09:08.710
We will pray over our

00:09:08.720 --> 00:09:11.750
firefighters and that

00:09:11.760 --> 00:09:14.870
all hidden things will be discovered

00:09:14.880 --> 00:09:17.590
concerning Chicago

00:09:17.600 --> 00:09:21.750
hotels in the days ahead.

00:09:25.519 --> 00:09:27.750
It

00:09:27.760 --> 00:09:30.470
was a very prominent,

00:09:30.480 --> 00:09:34.230
detailed vision. I

00:09:34.230 --> 00:09:34.240
also

00:09:34.240 --> 00:09:39.350
saw the

00:09:39.360 --> 00:09:42.870
river in New York with a massive

00:09:42.880 --> 00:09:45.990
building on the 41st floor; the

00:09:45.990 --> 00:09:46.000
Lord

00:09:46.000 --> 00:09:49.110
said

00:09:49.120 --> 00:09:53.030
this was more dominant than the

00:09:53.030 --> 00:09:53.040
other

00:09:53.040 --> 00:09:55.350
one. It was

00:09:55.350 --> 00:09:55.360
very foggy. It

00:09:55.360 --> 00:09:58.070
wasn't as

00:10:01.440 --> 00:10:04.070
crisp. I don't know how else to

00:10:04.080 --> 00:10:05.990
describe it, but that's the way it

00:10:06.000 --> 00:10:07.430
looked. And that's when the Lord said,

00:10:07.440 --> 00:10:09.190
"You're focusing more right now on

00:10:11.430 --> 00:10:11.440
Chicago."So,

00:10:14.160 --> 00:10:16.550
that's what we saw. And then we were

00:10:16.560 --> 00:10:21.350
shown a masquerade party. I saw many

00:10:21.360 --> 00:10:25.190
men and women in masquerade masks. They

00:10:25.200 --> 00:10:29.030
were in all kinds of rich,

00:10:29.040 --> 00:10:31.190
very

00:10:31.200 --> 00:10:33.030
thick,

00:10:33.040 --> 00:10:35.910
beautiful hooded robes

00:10:35.920 --> 00:10:39.350
that looked like white

00:10:39.350 --> 00:10:39.360
and

00:10:39.360 --> 00:10:42.630
black, and they had fur collars around

00:10:42.640 --> 00:10:46.550
some of them with detailed masks

00:10:46.550 --> 00:10:46.560
that were—some

00:10:46.560 --> 00:10:49.030
of them had long noses and

00:10:49.040 --> 00:10:51.509
some of them didn't—but all of them had

00:10:51.519 --> 00:10:53.990
some kind of drawing or jewels or

00:10:54.000 --> 00:10:57.350
something on their faces

00:10:57.360 --> 00:10:59.990
for rank or whatever. I

00:11:00.000 --> 00:11:01.110
don't know what it was. I don't want to

00:11:01.120 --> 00:11:04.230
assume anything. But I saw these masks

00:11:04.240 --> 00:11:06.710
on these people. And the Lord said,

00:11:06.720 --> 00:11:08.870
"Illuminati."Now,

00:11:08.880 --> 00:11:11.590
does that mean they're having

00:11:11.600 --> 00:11:14.389
parties with masks on? I don't know. Is

00:11:14.399 --> 00:11:17.509
it symbolic? Could be. All I know is

00:11:17.519 --> 00:11:19.110
what I see and what I tell you what I

00:11:19.120 --> 00:11:23.350
see. And as I was shown this, I saw

00:11:23.360 --> 00:11:25.910
these people with these hoods on

00:11:25.920 --> 00:11:29.030
across America,

00:11:29.040 --> 00:11:32.470
across Europe, across Mexico, and across

00:11:32.480 --> 00:11:33.670
Australia. There was a group in

00:11:33.680 --> 00:11:35.590
Australia. There were people

00:11:35.600 --> 00:11:37.910
that were attached to some kind of a

00:11:37.920 --> 00:11:42.790
cultic

00:11:42.800 --> 00:11:44.550
brotherhood

00:11:44.560 --> 00:11:46.790
that was celebrities,

00:11:46.800 --> 00:11:51.030
Hollywood

00:11:51.030 --> 00:11:51.040
celebrities,

00:11:51.040 --> 00:11:53.990
sports people,

00:11:54.000 --> 00:11:56.870
music industry, you name it. And they

00:11:56.880 --> 00:12:00.230
were all major players in our

00:12:00.240 --> 00:12:03.110
world economy and things that

00:12:03.120 --> 00:12:06.069
we do. I could see the celebrities.

00:12:06.079 --> 00:12:08.710
I could see the sports people. I

00:12:08.720 --> 00:12:10.389
could name their names. I'm not going

00:12:10.399 --> 00:12:13.670
to; that would be stupid. But I could

00:12:13.680 --> 00:12:16.310
see their faces and I could see them, and

00:12:16.320 --> 00:12:19.990
it was symbolic. As I was seeing this, I

00:12:20.000 --> 00:12:24.389
saw major political figures,

00:12:24.399 --> 00:12:26.389
and I even kind of hinted to who one of

00:12:26.399 --> 00:12:30.710
them was in a darker area.

00:12:30.720 --> 00:12:35.030
When this was shown to me, I saw

00:12:35.040 --> 00:12:36.949
"Anonymous."It

00:12:36.959 --> 00:12:39.829
was painted before my face in a word,

00:12:39.839 --> 00:12:43.990
and I saw another mask—"Anonymous."And I

00:12:44.000 --> 00:12:46.310
saw an individual

00:12:46.320 --> 00:12:48.710
concerning this, and I'm not going to

00:12:48.720 --> 00:12:51.750
describe it. It doesn't matter. But I saw

00:12:51.760 --> 00:12:55.670
this individual that was a hacker,

00:12:55.680 --> 00:12:58.949
a computer hacker that was some kind of

00:12:58.959 --> 00:13:03.110
elite computer hacker group. The

00:13:03.120 --> 00:13:05.670
Lord said that they would get in the

00:13:05.680 --> 00:13:08.949
days ahead—these kinds of hackers were

00:13:08.959 --> 00:13:10.870
going to get some kind of secret

00:13:10.880 --> 00:13:14.629
information concerning like

00:13:14.639 --> 00:13:17.430
Epstein list stuff

00:13:17.440 --> 00:13:23.350
to expose darkness in major arenas, and

00:13:23.360 --> 00:13:26.310
they wanted a ransom:

00:13:26.320 --> 00:13:28.870
big money. Over $40 million is what I

00:13:28.880 --> 00:13:31.910
was shown. Big bucks.

00:13:31.920 --> 00:13:33.750
Well, to me it's big bucks. Maybe to you

00:13:33.760 --> 00:13:35.910
it's not, but to me, that's

00:13:35.920 --> 00:13:38.310
crazy life-changing. $40 million

00:13:38.320 --> 00:13:40.790
is a lot of money, you know. But there

00:13:40.790 --> 00:13:40.800
are

00:13:40.800 --> 00:13:42.629
some of y'all out there who'd be like, "48

00:13:42.639 --> 00:13:44.389
million ain't nothing,

00:13:44.389 --> 00:13:44.399
Brandon."But

00:13:44.399 --> 00:13:46.949
to me, $40 million is

00:13:46.949 --> 00:13:46.959
a

00:13:46.959 --> 00:13:50.470
lot.

00:13:50.480 --> 00:13:52.949
I saw big money

00:13:52.959 --> 00:13:55.670
as a ransom for this,

00:13:55.680 --> 00:13:57.910
but they didn't get what they wanted.

00:13:57.920 --> 00:14:02.949
And I saw embarrassing

00:14:02.959 --> 00:14:07.990
moments coming for some celebrities. In

00:14:08.000 --> 00:14:11.350
particular, I saw a woman that was a

00:14:11.360 --> 00:14:13.829
First Lady that ran for president

00:14:13.839 --> 00:14:16.150
scrambling like a rat on

00:14:16.150 --> 00:14:16.160
a

00:14:16.160 --> 00:14:19.430
ship, like freaking out. I saw her face

00:14:19.440 --> 00:14:21.430
and she was freaking out for what was

00:14:21.440 --> 00:14:24.069
being leaked.

00:14:24.079 --> 00:14:27.269
She was the most dominant to me of

00:14:27.279 --> 00:14:30.870
anybody. Her husband that used to be

00:14:30.880 --> 00:14:33.189
president acted like he just couldn't care

00:14:33.199 --> 00:14:35.670
less. He acted like, "You know what?

00:14:35.680 --> 00:14:37.350
It's there. I'm old. What are you going

00:14:37.360 --> 00:14:39.665
to do about

00:14:39.675 --> 00:14:42.790
it?"Then

00:14:42.800 --> 00:14:47.670
I saw major key sports figures,

00:14:47.680 --> 00:14:51.670
huge people. I saw

00:14:51.680 --> 00:14:55.430
the Lakers. It was very bold. I saw the

00:14:55.440 --> 00:14:58.230
colors that were connected to this

00:14:58.240 --> 00:15:01.269
darkness.

00:15:01.279 --> 00:15:07.430
And I saw key figures with the Lakers,

00:15:07.440 --> 00:15:15.035
past and present;

00:15:15.045 --> 00:15:17.430
musicians

00:15:17.440 --> 00:15:21.509
that are here and some that are not.

00:15:21.519 --> 00:15:23.670
One of which I thought maybe I could say

00:15:23.680 --> 00:15:26.629
their name because he's dead,

