intimacy.

00:40:46.800 --> 00:40:51.270
You don't tell your secrets to somebody

00:40:51.280 --> 00:40:54.069
you don't trust.

00:40:54.079 --> 00:40:56.069
You tell your secrets to somebody that

00:40:56.079 --> 00:40:58.710
you're intimate with.

00:40:58.720 --> 00:41:01.270
Can God share His secrets with you? Are

00:41:01.280 --> 00:41:03.829
you intimate with Him? And that's what

00:41:03.839 --> 00:41:06.790
He said. You don't tell your secrets to

00:41:06.800 --> 00:41:08.230
anybody other than Dina because you're

00:41:08.240 --> 00:41:11.430
intimate with her. She's your friend;

00:41:11.440 --> 00:41:13.670
it's more than that—we have a covenant.

00:41:13.680 --> 00:41:15.430
There's nothing that

00:41:15.440 --> 00:41:17.109
she doesn't know about me, and there's

00:41:17.119 --> 00:41:19.910
nothing that I don't know about her.

00:41:19.920 --> 00:41:22.230
There is an intimacy in a

00:41:22.240 --> 00:41:25.030
marriage where you know everything about

00:41:25.040 --> 00:41:26.790
that individual.

00:41:26.800 --> 00:41:28.470
And that was what the Lord was saying to

00:41:28.480 --> 00:41:31.589
me: there's intimacy, and the more

00:41:31.599 --> 00:41:33.430
you're intimate with Me, I'll tell you

00:41:33.440 --> 00:41:35.990
the secret things.

00:41:36.000 --> 00:41:38.550
But I don't share intimacy with people

00:41:38.560 --> 00:41:41.430
who are not intimate with Me.

00:41:41.440 --> 00:41:44.230
Become intimate with Me and I will be

00:41:44.240 --> 00:41:46.470
intimate with you.

00:41:46.480 --> 00:41:48.870
I will show you that which is to

00:41:48.870 --> 00:41:48.880
come.

00:41:48.880 --> 00:41:51.030
You say, "Well, I don't hear Him.

00:41:51.040 --> 00:41:53.270
He doesn't talk to me about

00:41:53.280 --> 00:41:55.670
that kind of stuff. Are you any better

00:41:55.680 --> 00:41:58.870
than me, Brent?"No, no, no. My

00:41:58.880 --> 00:42:02.230
decisions have been different. Maybe

00:42:02.240 --> 00:42:03.910
my walk with the Lord has been

00:42:03.920 --> 00:42:06.230
different. I don't know the time you

00:42:06.240 --> 00:42:07.829
spend with Him. I don't try to

00:42:07.829 --> 00:42:07.839
say,

00:42:07.839 --> 00:42:09.750
"Well, I'm self-righteous; I

00:42:09.760 --> 00:42:11.750
spend all these hours a

00:42:11.750 --> 00:42:11.760
day."No,

00:42:11.760 --> 00:42:13.990
it's quality time. It's intimacy. It's

00:42:14.000 --> 00:42:15.430
allowing Him in your thought pattern.

00:42:15.440 --> 00:42:17.430
It's allowing Him into your inner circle

00:42:17.440 --> 00:42:20.550
and inviting Him daily,

00:42:20.560 --> 00:42:22.630
not just every once in a while. And it's

00:42:22.640 --> 00:42:24.790
obeying Him even whenever your flesh

00:42:24.800 --> 00:42:27.750
doesn't want to.

00:42:27.760 --> 00:42:30.790
Your flesh will scream

00:42:30.800 --> 00:42:32.550
whenever He tells you to give certain

00:42:32.560 --> 00:42:34.470
things away and do certain things, and

00:42:34.480 --> 00:42:36.710
you'll go, "I will not do

00:42:36.710 --> 00:42:36.720
this."But

00:42:36.720 --> 00:42:38.550
it's being faithful with little, and

00:42:38.560 --> 00:42:41.510
He'll make you ruler over much. Whenever

00:42:41.520 --> 00:42:43.750
you're faithful with the small thing,

00:42:43.760 --> 00:42:45.270
God will bless you with the bigger

00:42:45.280 --> 00:42:47.349
thing. But until you become faithful

00:42:47.359 --> 00:42:49.430
with the little, don't you ask Him for

00:42:49.440 --> 00:42:51.270
more?

00:42:51.280 --> 00:42:53.430
People always ask Him, "Well, how come I

00:42:53.440 --> 00:42:55.670
can't go from here to

00:42:55.670 --> 00:42:55.680
there?"It

00:42:55.680 --> 00:43:01.670
starts out with just five

00:43:01.670 --> 00:43:01.680
dollars.

00:43:01.680 --> 00:43:06.309
Can you be obedient with a dollar?

00:43:06.319 --> 00:43:10.550
Can you be obedient with a hundred

00:43:10.550 --> 00:43:10.560
dollars?

00:43:10.560 --> 00:43:14.150
If you cannot be obedient with a dollar,

00:43:14.160 --> 00:43:19.589
how does He take you to a

00:43:19.589 --> 00:43:19.599
hundred dollars?

00:43:19.599 --> 00:43:22.470
He will not share His secret things with

00:43:22.480 --> 00:43:26.309
people He cannot trust.

00:43:26.319 --> 00:43:29.910
Prove yourself trustworthy in these last

00:43:29.920 --> 00:43:31.430
days,

00:43:31.440 --> 00:43:33.670
and He will show you the secret

00:43:33.680 --> 00:43:36.710
things and the hidden things.

00:43:36.720 --> 00:43:38.550
Be faithful

00:43:38.560 --> 00:43:41.430
with what He's given you, honor it,

00:43:41.440 --> 00:43:44.230
and take care of it. I don't know how

00:43:44.240 --> 00:43:47.670
many times I would take our clunky car

00:43:47.680 --> 00:43:50.630
to the car wash and wax a car with the

00:43:50.640 --> 00:43:53.510
paint coming off

00:43:53.520 --> 00:43:55.430
or wrecked. People said, "Why don't you

00:43:55.440 --> 00:43:56.550
replace that bumper?"I didn't have the

00:43:56.560 --> 00:43:58.630
money to.

00:43:58.640 --> 00:44:00.390
The bumper was falling off of our Honda

00:44:00.400 --> 00:44:02.550
Accord, and we didn't have the

00:44:02.560 --> 00:44:03.510
money to fix it.

00:44:03.520 --> 00:44:04.710
We had it

00:44:04.710 --> 00:44:04.720
zip-tied.

00:44:04.720 --> 00:44:07.990
We fixed that thing

00:44:08.000 --> 00:44:10.710
with Diana. But I always waxed and took care

00:44:10.720 --> 00:44:13.030
of that car falling apart. Even when

00:44:13.040 --> 00:44:15.190
they repoed it

00:44:15.200 --> 00:44:16.870
because

00:44:16.880 --> 00:44:18.950
we couldn't make our payments, they took it from us. It

00:44:18.960 --> 00:44:21.510
was falling apart, and I remember they

00:44:21.510 --> 00:44:21.520
came—and

00:44:21.520 --> 00:44:23.589
it's bad when

00:44:23.599 --> 00:44:26.309
you get a car repoed from you when

00:44:26.319 --> 00:44:28.550
the front bumper's off and there's so

00:44:28.560 --> 00:44:30.309
much stuff going on with it—but I kept

00:44:30.319 --> 00:44:32.309
it clean.

00:44:32.319 --> 00:44:33.990
And when they came up there and took it,

00:44:34.000 --> 00:44:35.750
I kept it clean. And the guy goes, "Man,

00:44:35.760 --> 00:44:38.069
he took care of it.

00:44:38.069 --> 00:44:38.079
You tried."Amen.

00:44:38.079 --> 00:44:39.589
Even whenever

00:44:41.680 --> 00:44:43.670
the bank came in and took it

00:44:43.680 --> 00:44:46.630
from us, I

00:44:46.640 --> 00:44:50.069
took care of it.

00:44:50.079 --> 00:44:51.589
You've been faithful even

00:44:51.599 --> 00:44:53.270
with what God's given you.

00:44:53.280 --> 00:44:55.750
Even if it's not that

00:44:55.760 --> 00:44:57.430
nice,

00:44:57.440 --> 00:45:00.309
you always take care of it. And when you

00:45:00.319 --> 00:45:02.950
borrow somebody else's car, you make sure

00:45:02.960 --> 00:45:04.630
it's full of gas and clean when you

00:45:04.640 --> 00:45:07.510
return it.

00:45:07.520 --> 00:45:09.829
Don't return it dirty and with an

00:45:09.839 --> 00:45:12.950
empty tank of gas.

00:45:12.960 --> 00:45:17.829
Always do good unto others. Bless them.

00:45:17.839 --> 00:45:19.190
And that's what we've always tried to

00:45:19.200 --> 00:45:22.710
do. If Grandma ever lent us her van,

00:45:22.720 --> 00:45:24.870
I always made sure it was clean,

00:45:24.880 --> 00:45:26.630
vacuumed out, and full of gas when I

00:45:26.640 --> 00:45:28.069
returned it.

00:45:28.079 --> 00:45:28.630
Always.

00:45:28.640 --> 00:45:30.550
More gas than when we got it.

00:45:30.560 --> 00:45:31.270
Yes.

00:45:31.920 --> 00:45:34.630
Always treating people with

00:45:34.640 --> 00:45:36.550
respect when it comes to borrowing their

00:45:36.560 --> 00:45:39.030
stuff and honoring it when you get it.

00:45:39.040 --> 00:45:41.109
Don't return it back broken and don't

00:45:41.109 --> 00:45:41.119
return

00:45:41.119 --> 00:45:45.109
it back dirty.

00:45:45.119 --> 00:45:46.790
When you go into

00:45:46.800 --> 00:45:49.510
somebody's hotel room,

00:45:49.520 --> 00:45:52.950
don't leave it trashed.

00:45:52.960 --> 00:45:54.790
I always think somebody's going to have

00:45:54.800 --> 00:45:56.630
to come in here and clean this up. I

00:45:56.640 --> 00:45:58.230
clean it before they—hey, it was

00:45:58.240 --> 00:46:00.950
always nice and clean and not

00:46:00.960 --> 00:46:03.190
trashed. You go in there and don't steal

00:46:03.200 --> 00:46:06.710
their towels.

00:46:06.720 --> 00:46:07.990
"Well, you know what? I'm going to take the

00:46:07.990 --> 00:46:08.000
towel."No.

00:46:08.000 --> 00:46:12.550
Or the robe. You honor where

00:46:12.560 --> 00:46:17.510
you go. Show God wherever you go.

00:46:17.520 --> 00:46:19.349
Show people.

00:46:19.359 --> 00:46:21.030
That's what I try to do everywhere. Have

00:46:21.040 --> 00:46:23.910
integrity.

00:46:23.920 --> 00:46:27.270
Clean the church as if Jesus Himself

00:46:27.280 --> 00:46:29.670
was walking in there.

00:46:29.680 --> 00:46:33.430
Do it unto the Lord. And continue to

00:46:33.440 --> 00:46:36.630
do it. Whatever you do, do unto God. I

00:46:36.640 --> 00:46:38.150
did it every single time with

00:46:38.160 --> 00:46:39.910
everything. When you mow somebody's yard

00:46:39.920 --> 00:46:41.670
and they couldn't take care of it, I

00:46:41.680 --> 00:46:43.910
made it look like it was the best.

00:46:43.920 --> 00:46:45.430
Who's going to come? And I want it to

00:46:45.440 --> 00:46:50.230
