00:46:50.240 --> 00:46:53.109
Have integrity. Even mowing grass,

00:46:53.119 --> 00:46:56.390
pulling weeds, whatever you can do,

00:46:56.400 --> 00:47:01.990
have excellence in doing it.

00:47:04.079 --> 00:47:06.630
Cleanliness is godliness, you know.

00:47:06.640 --> 00:47:09.270
It

00:47:09.280 --> 00:47:10.950
doesn't take much for a bar of soap. You

00:47:10.960 --> 00:47:14.230
