00:47:18.240 --> 00:47:21.270
and smell like

00:47:21.280 --> 00:47:23.829
Zest or some Dove or whatever you got at

00:47:23.839 --> 00:47:27.589
the dollar store. But for my

00:47:27.599 --> 00:47:29.430
goodness, at least don't come to church

00:47:29.440 --> 00:47:31.750
and they go, "Man, he always smells like

00:47:31.760 --> 00:47:33.270
BO."I

00:47:33.280 --> 00:47:35.910
remember this guy; he always

00:47:35.920 --> 00:47:39.829
smells like body odor and a dirty

00:47:39.839 --> 00:47:41.750
bottom,

00:47:41.760 --> 00:47:44.069
and you go—and his hair is oily—but

00:47:44.069 --> 00:47:44.079
it doesn't

00:47:44.079 --> 00:47:47.030
cost much for a

00:47:47.040 --> 00:47:49.829
bar of soap.

00:47:49.839 --> 00:47:52.150
Do your best to try to take

00:47:52.160 --> 00:47:53.430
care of yourself because you

00:47:53.440 --> 00:47:56.470
